AFTER THE SEPTEMBER 11TH TERRORIST ATTACKS, THE U.S. INVADED AFGHANISTAN, REMOVING THE TALIBAN FROM POWER, BUT THEY NEVER OFFICIALLY LEFT THE REGION.
